戴夫与蒂科拉合作拍摄《Meridian》和《Special》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/dave-teams-up-with-tiakola-for-meridian-and-special-3488808?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=dave-teams-up-with-tiakola-经络特殊Emma WilkesFri, 25 Aug 2023 21:07:56 +0000 Music NewsNewsRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3488808 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dave-tiakola-pres.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="戴夫和蒂科拉" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dave-tiakola-pres.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dave-tiakola-pres-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dave-tiakola-pres-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dave-tiakola-pres-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dave-tiakola-pres-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dave-tiakola-pres-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这些歌曲是 Dave 与 Central Cee 破纪录合作《Sprinter》的后续歌曲</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dave-teams-up-with-tiakola-for-meridian-and-special-3488808">Dave 与 Tiakola 合作创作的《Meridian》和《Special》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dave-tiakola-pres.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="戴夫和蒂科拉" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dave-tiakola-pres.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dave-tiakola-pres-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dave-tiakola-pres-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dave-tiakola-pres-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dave-tiakola-pres-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dave-tiakola-pres-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dave">戴夫</a>与法国说唱歌手蒂亚科拉合作创作了两首新歌“Meridian”和“Special”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/dave-live-at-reading-festival-2022-review-3298929">Dave 在 2022 年雷丁节现场回顾：一套声明</a></strong></li></ul><p>在歌曲中，两位说唱歌手用英语、法语和约鲁巴语来回交换歌词，而《Meridian》则附有在巴黎、伦敦和纽约拍摄的视频。</p><p>看看下面的新曲目： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Tiakola x Dave - Meridian（官方剪辑）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/xalCsxC0WaE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="特别的" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/bWooZc8HKZ4?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这些歌曲是 Dave 与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/central-cee">Central Cee</a>破纪录合作的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-central-cee-and-dave-show-off-their-luxurious-lifestyle-in-sprinter-video-3451016">《Sprinter》</a>的后续歌曲，该歌曲在英国官方单曲排行榜上连续 10 周排名第一，并成为英国排行榜历史上持续时间最长的英国说唱歌曲。这首歌曲取自他们的联合 EP《Split Decision》，还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dave-and-central-cee-sprinter-is-spotify-uk-most-streamed-song-in-a-single-day-in-2023-so-far-3452500">打破了 Spotify UK 今年单日播放量最多的歌曲记录</a>。</p><p> Dave 最近还与 Oxlade 合作了歌曲“INTOXYCATED”，并与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/burna-boy">Burna Boy</a>重聚制作了歌曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/burna-boy-and-dave-bet-on-themselves-in-new-song-cheat-on-me-i-told-them-album-3487430">“Cheat On Me”</a> 。今年早些时候，他与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fredo">Fredo</a>合作制作了一首<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stormzy">Stormzy</a>单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/stormzy-returns-with-new-dave-produced-fredo-collaboration-toxic-trait-3459858">“Toxic Trait”</a> 。</p><p>这些专辑是继去年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dave-shares-video-for-wavy-new-track-starlight-3175426">《Starlight》</a>和《My 24thbirthday》之后发行的，前者是他在英国的第一首个人单曲，也是继 2018 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fredo">弗雷多</a>协助的《Funky Friday》之后的第二张专辑。</p><p> 2019年，戴夫发行了首张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/dave-psychodrama-review-2460042">《Psychodrama》</a> ，该专辑获得<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/mercury">水星奖</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2020-winners-list-2611390">2020年全英音乐奖</a>年度专辑奖。这位斯特里汉姆说唱歌手随后推出了荣获 MOBO 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/brits">全英音乐</a>奖的 2021 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/dave-were-all-alone-in-this-together-review-3001456">“We’re All Alone in This Together”</a> 。 2021 年，Central Cee 还发行了他的首张混音带《6 For 6》，去年，他发行了他的排行榜冠军混音<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/central-cee-23-mixtape-review-radar-3168978">带《23》，</a>其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pinkpantheress">PinkPantheress</a>采样热门歌曲《Obsessed With You》。他还在七月发行了迄今为止播放量最大的歌曲“Doja”，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/central-cee-drops-surprise-ep-no-more-leaks-shares-video-for-one-up-3329182">令人惊喜的 EP“No More Leaks</a> ”。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dave-teams-up-with-tiakola-for-meridian-and-special-3488808">Dave 与 Tiakola 合作创作的《Meridian》和《Special》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
鲍勃·迪伦中心宣布新的年度歌曲作者奖学金https://www.nme.com/news/music/bob-dylan-center-announces-new-annual-songwriter-fellowship-3488807?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=bob-dylan-center-announces-new-annual-作曲家联谊会Hollie GeraghtyFri, 25 Aug 2023 21:07:22 +0000 Music NewsNewsFolkRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3488807 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/bob-dylan-songwriter-award.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="鲍勃·迪伦" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/bob-dylan-songwriter-award.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/bob-dylan-songwriter-award-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/bob-dylan-songwriter-award-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/bob-dylan-songwriter-award-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/bob-dylan-songwriter-award-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/bob-dylan-songwriter-award-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>两名歌曲作者将获得年度奖项，其中包括 40,000 美元（31,784 英镑）的津贴</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bob-dylan-center-announces-new-annual-songwriter-fellowship-3488807">鲍勃·迪伦中心宣布新的年度歌曲作者奖学金的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/bob-dylan-songwriter-award.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="鲍勃·迪伦" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/bob-dylan-songwriter-award.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/bob-dylan-songwriter-award-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/bob-dylan-songwriter-award-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/bob-dylan-songwriter-award-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/bob-dylan-songwriter-award-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/bob-dylan-songwriter-award-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bob-dylan">鲍勃·迪伦</a>中心与环球音乐出版集团合作推出了新的年度歌曲作者奖学金。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/bob-dylan-rough-and-rowdy-ways-album-review-2688344">鲍勃·迪伦（Bob Dylan）——《粗暴的方式》评论：可以说是他迄今为止最伟大的诗意陈述</a></strong></li></ul><p>该奖学金于周三（8 月 23 日）宣布，每年将向两名获奖者颁发 40,000 美元（31,784 英镑）的项目津贴，以及公众参与和演讲机会、在鲍勃·迪伦档案馆的时间、指导、在莱昂·拉塞尔历史悠久的教堂工作室的工作室时间塔尔萨的往返机票及更多信息。</p><p>评审小组成员包括美国说唱歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/aritsts/nas">纳斯</a>、朱丽叶·阿玛内特、帕蒂·格里芬、约翰·梅伦坎普和卡拉·莫里森等音乐家和词曲作者，以及 BDC 和 UMPG 的高管。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CwTQ1l_ps58/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fi